        <updateDate>2020-12-14T19:14:21Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Retirement Investments for a Sustainable Economy Act of 2020 or the RISE Act of </b><b>2020</b></p> <p>This bill establishes a new fund&#8212;the Climate Choice Stock Index Fund&#8212;as an investment option under the Thrift Savings Plan.</p> <p>The Climate Choice Stock Index Fund must be invested in a portfolio that is designed to replicate the performance of a commonly recognized index comprised of common stock and to ensure that no investment in the portfolio is an investment in a fossil fuel entity.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
